scene.message:
Brown: H-hey, Toro!{nl}
I'm sorry for hiding the{nl}
food from you, okay?{waitkey}{clearbox}Please, don't eat any more!{nl}
What a waste!!{waitkey}{ret}

Student: Sorry, man.{nl}
I figured if you found it,{nl}
you'd eat the whole lot.{waitkey}{clearbox}We've gotta ration it -{nl}
the school's in a crisis{nl}
right now! Understand?{waitkey}{ret}

Toro: Sh-shut uuup!!{nl}
You're all making fun of me!{waitkey}{clearbox}You were splitting the food{nl}
behind my back, weren't you!{nl}
Damn it, I'll stress-eat!!{waitkey}{ret}

{color:2}Kenta Yokouchi, a.k.a.{nl}
"Toro." Loves to eat.{nl}
Strong, but timid.{color:0}{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: That's precious food!{nl}
You get dumped and throw a{nl}
fit, and we all starve?{waitkey}{clearbox}Aw, is my brilliant life{nl}
gonna end like this?{nl}
A suicide pact with a fatso...{waitkey}{ret}

Toro: Aaaaaaah{waitkey}F-f-f-fat... Don't{nl}
call me faaaat!!{waitkey}{clearbox}Daaaamn it!{waitkey}Before I starve, I'll eat!{nl}
Eat and eat and stock up!{waitkey}{clearbox}I'll watch you all{nl}
drop dead one by one!{waitkey}Uha uha uha uhaa!{waitkey}{ret}

Student: H-hey...{nl}
his eyes have gone wild.{nl}
What now, Brown?{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Wh-what do you mean,{nl}
what now?!{waitkey}Damn it, Ayase!{nl}
This is 'cause you{nl}
dumped him!!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Hey, hold on~!{nl}
Why's this Ayase's{nl}
fault~?!{waitkey}{ret}

Toro: Aha aha ahaa~{nl}
It's no use~{waitkey}{clearbox}I've got a Demon the{nl}
butterfly gave me!{waitkey}{clearbox}I'm not a lump of meat{nl}
anymore, Ayase!{waitkey}Uha uha uhaa!{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: A Demon~?{nl}
This guy's lost it - cracked{nl}
from the shock of heartbreak.{waitkey}{ret}

Student: I'll go get{nl}
a teacher!{nl}
Keep watch till then!{waitkey}{ret}

Toro: Uha uha uha uha uha{nl}
No matter how many of you,{nl}
you can't stop me!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Calm down, Yokouchi!{waitkey}{clearbox}When the town's restored,{nl}
I'll have my chef feed you{nl}
a feast till you burst!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Toro!{nl}
Why are you doing this?!{waitkey}{clearbox}This makes it look like{nl}
Ayase's the bad guy!!{waitkey}{ret}

Toro: Ahh, my dear Ayase!{nl}
If you'll go out with me,{nl}
I'll spare you alone!{waitkey}{clearbox}I'll set aside your{nl}
share of the food!{waitkey}Uha uha uhaa!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Denied.{wait_fr:32}{nl}
The worst.{wait_fr:32}{nl}
Hard pass.{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: H-hey, don't provoke{nl}
him! You're too blunt, Yuka.{waitkey}{clearbox}When he confessed, you said{nl}
something harsh too, right?!{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Boss lady!{waitkey}{clearbox}Looks like he won't snap{nl}
out of it unless you give{nl}
him a good thrashing!{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Who're you calling{nl}
boss lady?! You've got{nl}
some nerve. Save that{nl}
for a last resort.{waitkey}{clearbox}For now, let's buy time{nl}
until a teacher comes!{waitkey}{clearbox}C'mon, Uesugi!{nl}
Quit standing there{nl}
in a daze{waitkey}and lend a hand!!{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Dehyahyahyahya!{nl}
I'll follow you to the{nl}
ends of the earth!{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Boo hoo...{nl}
What a thing to{nl}
say to me!!{waitkey}{clearbox}It's not too late!{nl}
Apologize!{nl}
Just apologize!!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: No wonder Yokouchi's{nl}
angry.{waitkey}Truly, the mouth is the{nl}
root of misfortune...{waitkey}{clearbox}You went too far, Ayase!{nl}
Apologize.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Ehh~?!{nl}
Did I go too far?{waitkey}{clearbox}Hey, Toro,{nl}
did the truth hurt you?{waitkey}{ret}

Toro: Ngh...{nl}
Ayase, you really are...{waitkey}{clearbox}The price for hurting my{nl}
pure heart is a heavy one~{waitkey}{clearbox}Demon, oh Demon,{nl}
please come forth!{waitkey}{clearbox}Come out and punish{nl}
all those who made{nl}
fun of me!!{waitkey}{clearbox}......binburu...{wait_fr:30}banburu...{nl}
...{wait_fr:30}bamboppun...{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Hey hey hey hey hey,{nl}
what're you chanting, Toro?{waitkey}{clearbox}Doing that won't... what is{nl}
this, a manga?{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: ?{nl}
What's he chanting?{waitkey}{clearbox}You're a high schooler -{nl}
quit dreaming about{nl}
"Demons"...{waitkey}{ret}
